>> time required: 60 minutes
>> course: main

Cut @whole chicken{1} add @salt and @vinegar{1%tbsp}
Let sit ~{30%minutes}
Boil @water{2%cups}, then add @red curry paste{1%cup}
Once boiling add the chicken and sliced in 2 @kaffir lime leaves{20}
boil for ~{15%minutes}
Add @green beans{250%g}, (most of the water should be reduced)
Add @coconut milk{3%cups}, bring to boil
Simmer for ~{10%minutes}
Add leaves of @thai basil{1%bunch}
Season with @salt
Take of heat
